name: "Trippy 2" - "Trip Art"
description: “Trip Art” is the digital collection of the Brazilian artist Ana Braga in which she manipulates her images through artificial intelligence. The artist merges photographs and her original works painted on canvas and paper, creating unique and vibrant images, a true “Trip” between forms, colors, the real and the imaginary abstract. These digital artistic works celebrates Ana Braga's more than 15 years in the art market, in Brazil and abroad.@anabragaart;anabraga.art.br;https://linktr.ee/Ana_Braga
